03c/header\u003e\n\n                            \n        \n\n        \n                                        \n                                \n            \n                        \n        \n        \n\n    \n            \n    \n                                                            \n            \n    \n               \n    \n                    \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n                                                    \n                        \n    \n                                                                            \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                                                    \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                                    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                    \n            \n    \n    \n        \n                    \n                        \n                                    \n\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_0\"\u003e\n\u003ch3\u003eKey Takeaways\u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e \n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e YouTube is experimenting with hiding view counts and upload dates on the homepage. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e Speculation behind the motive includes a cleaner UI encouraging interest in non-viral content. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e Users are divided on the potential changes, expressing a range of reactions — almost none entirely positive. \u003c/li\u003e\n \u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eEverybody loves a good interface shakeup, right?\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYouTube\u0026#39;s latest test involves hiding both view counts \u003cem\u003eand\u003c/em\u003e upload dates when first loading up your homepage (via \u003ca href=\"https://www.dexerto.com/youtube/youtube-reportedly-testing-new-homepage-that-removes-dates-and-view-counts-2965695/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eDexerto\u003c/a\u003e). At the moment, the test isn\u0026#39;t widespread, although early user reactions range from, \u0026#34;I don\u0026#39;t think this will help,\u0026#34; to, \u0026#34;Downgrade of the century.\u0026#34; Naturally, there\u0026#39;s no word on the reasoning behind the potential change, but speculation includes both the \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/youtubes-war-against-third-party-apps-is-ridiculous/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003equest for a cleaner UI\u003c/a\u003e, and an attempt to get viewers clicking on \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-podcast-apps/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003econtent that isn\u0026#39;t yet viral\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"youtube-is-on-a-roll-with-interface-changes\"\u003e YouTube is on a roll with interface changes \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"experiments-are-where-they-start-for-better-or-worse\"\u003e Experiments are where they start, for better or worse \u003c/h3\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;Source: @vidIQ on Twitter\\/X via Dexerto\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A screenshot of YouTube\u0026#39;s homepage test without view counts or upload dates\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/youtube-homepage-test-no-view-counts-upload-date.jpeg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eSource: @vidIQ on Twitter/X via Dexerto\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e The newly discovered trial balloon comes on the heels of busy month at Google\u0026#39;s streaming behemoth. Some, like the \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/youtube-android-new-miniplayer-wide-rollout/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eapp\u0026#39;s updated miniplayer\u003c/a\u003e, garnered (rightful) praise, while the \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/youtube-hiding-skip-button-mobile/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eobscured Skip Ads button\u003c/a\u003e saw a friendly back-and-forth between Android Police and Google, with the latter ensuring us that the button\u0026#39;s not \u003cem\u003ehidden\u003c/em\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/youtube-skip-ads-rebuttal/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eit\u0026#39;s just \u003cem\u003ebehind something else\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/a\u003e so it doesn\u0026#39;t distract you from the ads. And that\u0026#39;s to say nothing of the potentially manipulative YouTube Shorts (or \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/youtube-shorts-video-duration-bump/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eis it YouTube Pants\u003c/a\u003e?) \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/youtube-shorts-ui-tweak-dislike-save-buttons/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003edislike/save button location swap\u003c/a\u003e or comment-busying hyperlinks addition.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"b043-4bde-ace816e78c8f\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/top-hidden-youtube-features/\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003cimg width=\"3000\" height=\"1688\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A phone showing the YouTube logo on a colorful background\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/youtube-features-1.jpg\"/\u003e \u003c/picture\u003e \u003c/figure\u003e \u003c/div\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003ePlayful derision aside, it\u0026#39;s not a stretch to imagine the removal of view counts helping broaden people\u0026#39;s choices, since it\u0026#39;s all too easy to flock to the most popular videos the moment the homepage loads. Obscuring upload dates makes a little less sense, as the most dedicated and prolific YouTube viewers typically live for the most up-to-date videos.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOn the other hand, everybody misses things sometimes. We could be convinced that cutting upload dates from the front page will help users engage with content that might not be the \u003cem\u003emost \u003c/em\u003erecent, but is still relevant on a given day. That is, of course, dependent on YouTube not altering the algorithm to push videos far past their prime.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAs you might imagine, there\u0026#39;s no word on motive behind the test, or how close it is to the general public\u0026#39;s reality. If user reaction is anything to go by, YouTube would do well to steer clear of implementing it permanently. While some social media users were understanding of view counts getting the axe, and others didn\u0026#39;t mind upload dates going away, extremely few come out in full-throated support of YouTube latest, mysterious test.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n    \n        \n\n    \n\n        \n\n\n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        